title: Join us for OpenAI’s first developer conference on November 6 in San Francisco
summary: OpenAI is hosting its first developer conference, OpenAI DevDay, on November 6, 2023 in San Francisco. The event aims to bring together developers from around the world to preview new tools and exchange ideas. Attendees will have the opportunity to join breakout sessions led by OpenAI's technical staff. OpenAI's API, which includes advanced models like GPT-4, GPT-3.5, DALL·E, and Whisper, has been widely adopted by over 2 million developers for various use cases. The conference will showcase OpenAI's latest work in enabling developers to build new applications and services. Interested individuals can visit devday.openai.com for more information and sign up for notifications about registration. Press members can contact devdaypress@openai.com for attendance inquiries.
